Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi,\N are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, two people rose up on the Fish-Man Island,\N to change our hopeless history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One was Queen Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other is the hero who \Nfreed the slaves - Fisher Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk. They were two\N monumental figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was their hidden angst?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:13.98,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Hero Who Freed the Slaves!\N An Adventurer Tiger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an incident that made Arlong \Nrampage through the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you especially to know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all began...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...16 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:58.73,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}16 YEARS AGO - THE FISH-MAN ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stole a lot of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If anyone comes close, you won't \Nwanna see what I'll do with this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Your Majesty! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away! Or I'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I warned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:24.56,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}KING NEPTUNE'S WIFE\NQUEEN OTOHIME (GOLDFISH MERMAID)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ouch!\N--Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My hand!\N--Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness! Let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a compound fracture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With one hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you done such a senseless\N thing as robbing someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're from a wealthy,\N royal family - you don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have 10 kids at home, \Nwho are crying from hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the more reason to not do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Queen-sama! Stop hitting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far more fragile than all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! I have to do this for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to teach him even if it \Nshatters my hand into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would your children be happy \Nbeing raised by stolen money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live a life of which your\N children can be proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to... apologize, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice your struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I'm your queen and \NI'm living in the same country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your worries and your pain are killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have had some awful\N reason to do what you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My store burned down. \NSomebody set fire to it and stole all my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my job and my debts were increasing.\N And my poor kids were starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you did it. I understand...\N I understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But you can't do that!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do the same thing to others,\N it will never stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry! We are guilty\N of not being dependable...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very generous...\N That's very generous of you to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will change my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for crying for a \Ngood-for-nothing like me, Queen-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already unusual for someone from \Nthe royal family to come out of the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and walk around...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to slap a citizen and sob over his story!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama is a very \Nunconventional queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a woman of boundless compassion.\N Look, even kids love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do my best for you children!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is running! \NI hit you for your own good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a fool having \Nsnot running out of one nostril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to have to come from both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so passionate and \Nfull of love. Queen Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...went down to the island everyday\N and addressed the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to relocate the \NRyugu Kingdom on earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a different skin color.\N We look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what humans say. And instead of waiting\N for the day when they'll understand us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should move closer to \Nthem to understand them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seafloor is 10,000 meters from the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is also the distance \Nbetween our ways of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The humans who come to this island\N are the kind called "pirates."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the humans who buy people from \Nkidnappers are the Nobles who are in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only known the bad sort of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything about humans yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many kind \Nhumans on earth, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should relocate the \Nkingdom under the same sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's express our intention to \Nrelocate at the World Summit this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you all to sign here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if it's Otohime-sama's idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of moving closer \Nto humans is... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take the first step \Ninstead of doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. History has proven it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shirahoshi, my consolation.\N I'm sorry to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:13:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your nose is running \Nbut you're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were here with her so \Nshe was safe, mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was safe, she was safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, my princes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama, is your hand okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that you four will live in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will change it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Otohime-sama wants to make a speech,\N she could do it by video.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her strong Observation Haki by \Nnature makes her the way she is-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She prefers to face people to win their hearts\N rather than speak from the palace above.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of Otohime's guiding principles.\N And not even I can stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are a lot of human \Npirates staying on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is protected by your friend, the pirate \N- Whitebeard's influence to some extent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you never know what could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world that Otohime dreams about is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...exactly the same as...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what our ancestors dreamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but couldn't make come true \Nseveral hundred years ago-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to keep her safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, fish girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes?\N--Stay here and serve us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. We don't do that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't be such a snob!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a Fish-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Does anyone have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make my sake taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:32.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE RYUGU KINGDOM - A SOLDIER OF NEPTUNE'S ARMY\NJIMBEI     30 YEARS OLD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Otohime-san was a very unusual woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a crybaby just like your mother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you a soldier of the kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't that many options for\N a man from the Fish-Man District...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who knew nothing but fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Man District?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you're from, right, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a bad neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It used to be a big orphanage where they\N housed children without any relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the orphanage started\N to get out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was too much for the \Nadministrators to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it became a lawless area that drew\N misfits from all over the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tiger was the leader \Nfigure in the Fish-Man District
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he left the country to chase adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was his lieutenant but\N I joined Neptune's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Macro and the others became kidnappers \Neven though they were Fish-Men themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the others went \Ntheir separate ways as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give them back! Please!\N--Take them if you want them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them back to her! Do you know \Nhow many signatures there are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do with these papers? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut it out! You're Arlong from \Nthe Fish-Man District, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong from the Fish-Man District?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bit wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:36.82,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE CAPTAIN OF THE ARLONG PIRATES\NARLONG 25     YEARS OLD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:41.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Captain Arlong from the Arlong Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make a living by hunting those lowly \Npirates who can't even breathe in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing it on behalf of \Nall of you - Neptune's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me with your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss Jimbei, don't just watch - help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, punk! Let go of that rookie soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is my man, in a way.\NAnd the papers with signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in them but they're \Nimportant for the Queen. So give them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's Boss Jimbei of Neptune's army!\N--Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Boss"? That's a good title.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're running a gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as I say, Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mad, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, huh? I'm your \Nfamily from the Fish-Man District!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like you. \NYou're still a pirate, aren't you, scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't call me "scum," brother!\N--How about trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Trash"?! I've let you say \Nwhat you wanted, but that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everybody! It's the \Nadventurer - Fisher Tiger-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Tiger-san's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tiger-san!\N--How was the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Brother Tai!\N--Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei! Arlong! \NLooks like you guys are doing fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long trip, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop by at my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe later. I need to go \Nto the Ryugu Palace first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you then. \NHe doesn't have use for a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Big Brother wouldn't say such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to free the slaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am serious. I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a living hell \Nto be a slave isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we speak now, they are not\N being treated like men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to tell you \Nand the Queen in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since it will cause you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell anybody about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see during your trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then before long,\N something big happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss Jimbei! T-Tiger-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...attacked the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Dragons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tiger's attack on \Nthe Holyland of Marie Jois!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People called him the hero \Nwho freed the slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the same time, he became a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the army today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei, are you going to \Nwalk away from your mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly, I enjoyed my \Nrole of protecting the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, paying a debt \Nof honor is more important
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:22:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than carrying out my mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Tai did it at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Arlong Pirates will \Njoin Fisher Tiger now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was how the ruffians \Nfrom the Fish-Man District
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who admired him assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the pirates' world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight against the world from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who are ready, come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make it \Nimpossible to distinguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between those who were \Nslaves and those who weren't,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everybody used the Sun mark to \Ncover over the mark of slaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:23:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Sun Pirates \Nwere formed by Fish-Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tiger attacked the \NHolyland of Marie Jois
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and freed Fish-Man slaves \Nfrom the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pursued by the Marines, they fight the \Nhumans in battle after bloody battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until he has a fateful encounter with \Na human girl with a painful past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a certain man finally makes his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kizaru Appears!\NA Trap to Catch Tiger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
